The mention of upper bounds on the speed and effectiveness of compression also suggests that the paper may belong to cs.CC (Computational Complexity) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the use of variable-length codeword encodings suggests that the paper may belong to cs.DC (Data Compression).
